sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant W as Web/Mobile App
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant E as Expense Service
    participant B as Bus (Event Bus)
    participant BAL as Balance Service
    participant N as Notification Service

    U->>W: Fill expense (amount, payers, split, category)
    W->>G: POST /expenses (with login badge)
    G->>E: Create expense
    Note over E: Check payers sum = total<br/>Check split sum = total
    E->>E: Save to Expense DB
    E-->>G: 201 Created (expense)
    G-->>W: Saved
    E->>B: Publish "expense.added" (the bell)
    B->>BAL: Deliver "expense.added"
    BAL->>BAL: Recalculate balances (read model)
    B->>N: Deliver "expense.added"
    N->>N: Make notices for group members
    Note over W,BAL: Balance is eventually consistent:<br/>tiny lag after save before tally updates
